CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

February 1, 2005

[Cite as 02/01/200S Case Announcements, 2005-Ohio-330.]

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2004-1259. State v. Taylor.

Madison App. No. CA2003-07-025, 2004-Ohio-3171. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Madison County.

IT IS ORDERED by the court, sua sponte, that this cause is held for the decisions in 2004-1771, State v. Quinones, Cuyahoga App. No. 83720, 2004-Ohio-4485, and 2004-1568, State v. Foster, Licking App. No. 03CA95, 2004-Ohio-4209.

IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that the briefing schedule remains stayed.
